<item>
            <title>[TEXT-76] Jaro Winkler implementation is not correct</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TEXT-76</link>
                <project id="12318221" key="TEXT">Commons Text</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Using 3.5 commons-lang the following call return a distance of 1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;StringUtils.getJaroWinklerDistance(&#8220;/opt/software1&#8221;,  &#8220;/opt/software2&#8221;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Jaro Winkler says that distance of 1 means equal string which is not the case here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13061117">TEXT-76</key>
            <summary>Jaro Winkler implementation is not correct</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
